OL,3,CWoman says ex-boyfriend stalked her
OL,4,Cfor a year before she sought help
OL,6,F'Sarah' says she was being stalked for
OL,7,Fover a year before she realised that's
OL,8,Fwhat was happening.
OL,10,FA Sussex woman who thought she'd found
OL,11,Fher soulmate said he later became her
OL,12,Fstalker.
OL,14,FThey'd been together for 11 years, but
OL,15,Fshe decided to leave when he started
OL,16,Fabusing substances.
OL,18,FSarah, not her real name, said he just
OL,19,Fturned and started texting her
OL,20,Fconstantly.
