OL,3,CWoman says ex-boyfriend stalked her
OL,4,Cfor a year before she sought help
OL,6,F"I think some people still think
OL,7,Fsometimes that it is people following
OL,8,Fyou around and looking through
OL,9,Fwindows, which isn't always the case."
OL,11,F"There are lots of ways that people
OL,12,Fstalk people, they can include mobile
OL,13,Fphones and calls and texts, turning up
OL,14,Fat addresses, tracking devices."
OL,16,F"There is also a digital element as
OL,17,Fwell, use of social media and apps on
OL,18,Fphones to also stalk and cause harm to
OL,19,Fthe victims."
