OL,6,FThe force uses a behavioural
OL,7,Fintervention programme to help prevent
OL,8,Freoffending.
OL,10,F"The vast majority of those who
OL,11,Fcomplete the programme don't go on to
OL,12,Freoffend," she said.
OL,14,FDS Bartup wants to encourage victims
OL,15,Fto come forward so they can get
OL,16,Fsupport and offenders can be stopped.
